%spark
import org.apache.spark.sql.types._
import org.apache.spark.sql.functions.{concat, lit}

import org.datasyslab.geospark.spatialOperator.RangeQuery
import org.datasyslab.geospark.spatialRDD.PointRDD
import org.datasyslab.geospark.spatialOperator.JoinQuery
import org.datasyslab.geospark.spatialRDD.RectangleRDD
import com.vividsolutions.jts.geom.Envelope
import org.datasyslab.geospark.spatialOperator.KNNQuery
import org.datasyslab.geospark.spatialRDD.PointRDD
import org.datasyslab.geospark.spatialRDD.PolygonRDD
import com.vividsolutions.jts.geom.Coordinate
import com.vividsolutions.jts.geom.GeometryFactory
import com.vividsolutions.jts.geom.Point

val df = sqlContext
  .read
  .format("org.apache.spark.sql.cassandra")
  .options(Map( "table" -> "tweets_hamburg_located", "keyspace" -> "master_dataset" ))
  .load()  

val df2 = df.filter($"year".equalTo(date_format(current_timestamp, "yyyy")))
            .filter($"month".equalTo(date_format(current_timestamp, "MM")))
            .filter($"geolocationlatitude".isNotNull)
            .filter($"geolocationlatitude".between(53.400000, 53.750000) )
            .filter($"geolocationlongitude".between(9.650000, 10.370000) )
            .selectExpr(
                "tweetId",
                "createdAt",
                "userName",
                "text",
                "concat(geolocationlatitude, ',', geolocationlongitude)",
                "cast(geolocationlatitude as double) lat", 
                "cast(geolocationlongitude as double) lan")
//df2.show()          
//var msg = dataValidatorSrv.validateMapData(df2)            
z.show(df2)

paragraphs.title: Daily tweets located in Hamburg (Spark)
paragraphs.text:
%spark
val df = sqlContext
  .read
  .format("org.apache.spark.sql.cassandra")
  .options(Map( "table" -> "tweets_counter_hourly", "keyspace" -> "master_dataset" ))
  .load()
  
val df2 = df.filter($"year".equalTo(date_format(current_timestamp, "yyyy")) || $"year".equalTo(date_format(current_timestamp - expr("INTERVAL 2 MONTH"), "yyyy")))
            .filter($"month".equalTo(date_format(current_timestamp, "MM")) || $"month".equalTo(date_format(current_timestamp - expr("INTERVAL 1 MONTH"), "MM")) || $"month".equalTo(date_format(current_timestamp - expr("INTERVAL 2 MONTH"), "MM")))
            .filter($"table_name".equalTo("tweets_hamburg") || $"table_name".equalTo("tweets_hamburg_located"))
         //   .filter($"lang".equalTo("de") || $"lang".equalTo("en") )
          //  .filter($"tweets_counter">20)
            .selectExpr("table_name",
                        "year", 
                        "month", 
                        "day", 
                        "hour", 
                        "tweets_counter")
            
            
z.show(df2)

paragraphs.title: Daily tweets located in Hamburg (Spark; using daily counter)
paragraphs.text:
%spark
val df = sqlContext
  .read
  .format("org.apache.spark.sql.cassandra")
  .options(Map( "table" -> "tweets_counter_daily", "keyspace" -> "master_dataset" ))
  .load()
  
val df2 =   df.filter($"year".equalTo(date_format(current_timestamp, "yyyy")) || $"year".equalTo(date_format(current_timestamp - expr("INTERVAL 2 MONTH"), "yyyy")))
            .filter($"month".equalTo(date_format(current_timestamp, "MM")) || $"month".equalTo(date_format(current_timestamp - expr("INTERVAL 1 MONTH"), "MM")) || $"month".equalTo(date_format(current_timestamp - expr("INTERVAL 2 MONTH"), "MM")))
            .filter($"table_name".equalTo("tweets_hamburg") || $"table_name".equalTo("tweets_hamburg_located"))
         //   .filter($"lang".equalTo("de") || $"lang".equalTo("en") )
         //   .filter($"tweets_counter">20)
            .selectExpr("table_name",
                        "year", 
                        "month", 
                        "day",  
                        "tweets_counter")
            
            
z.show(df2)
